{"tid":1458651,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"不流血！不受傷！不被捕！今日我哋真係做到。","createTime":"2019-08-12T14:35:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T14:05:55.000Z","uid":2565,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ac9850da32cca48193ae1a8e920a94db3c6c9811","tid":1458651,"uid":2565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:35:40.000Z","msg":"你知道嗎？為甚麼走為上計，會被排到三十六計嗎？<br />\n<br />\n其實古時戰爭，<br />\n最可怕嘅並唔係一兩場戰役嘅輸贏，<br />\n而係我哋因為一場戰役而完全失去士氣，<br />\n押上所有戰鬥人員然後全盤覆滅。<br />\n<br />\n逃跑被視為計謀一種，<br />\n是將「失敗」轉化為戰術，<br />\n所謂敗仗是將軍胸有成竹、計算在內的一著，<br />\n我們利用失敗誘敵。<br />\n現代戰爭，<br />\n尚有「戰略轉進」一詞，<br />\n係我軍完成戰略目標之後，<br />\n轉而進軍到其他地方（如返屋企瞓覺），<br />\n係保存戰力一種最有效方法。<br />\n<br />\n記住，應退則退，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我們絕對可以撤退、毫無保留地撤退，</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最重要是我們毫不間斷的回來。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n敵進我退，<br />\n敵駐我擾，<br />\n大家記住今日一仗。"},{"pid":"fdccba4f0f37750a1bc0c8af19698c02751a40e2","tid":1458651,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:38:27.000Z","msg":"[賽後檢討] 抗爭者進化史<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1458526\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1458526</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"34de644438297afebabbc1f7c70cff6174b487de","tid":1458651,"uid":2565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:39:48.000Z","msg":"戰略轉進 保持實力！"},{"pid":"cd7ae8709795d10fb25f894f3e4b3c9fa1296fad","tid":1458651,"uid":31320,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:40:24.000Z","msg":"[是日戰績] 半日政府損失 二千五百萬財務業績<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1458428\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1458428</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唔好再塞鐵塞路<br />\n低效率高風險<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港，得一個國際機場<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n緊記：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有旅客就去，冇旅客就退</span></span>"},{"pid":"eaaffeef2d3f98ea1de289f1bac0defdc878585e","tid":1458651,"uid":2565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:42:38.000Z","msg":"612！721！811！"},{"pid":"c1ca392ede0b85da7b99be0806ef626ec61f4287","tid":1458651,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:42:47.000Z","msg":"[緊急分析]法！不！責！眾！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1456781\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1456781</a>"},{"pid":"26fa11e2deeb7007c012a94d440f78a536913302","tid":1458651,"uid":147916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:05:55.000Z","msg":"羊巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}